  <description><![CDATA[<p>Situated in the impressive Stelvio National Park, Bormio offers a wonderful combination of a charming town which has retained its Italian character and a ski area that is worthy of its world champion status. In the village you can stroll along the cobbled streets of the old market town which has an array of interesting shops bars and restaurants.  Add to this an extensive and efficient ski lift system which has superb connections and well maintained pistes and lots of varied skiing.  Bormio has all the ingredients for a wonderful ski holiday.</p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
